@JoyBoxPlatform_HostAddress = http://localhost:5098

### Get all games
GET {{JoyBoxPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/games
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific game by ID
GET {{JoyBoxPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/games/1
Accept: application/json

### Upload a game (replace path/to/file.zip)
POST {{JoyBoxPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/games/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

My First Game
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

A simple test game.
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="zipFile"; filename="game.zip"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./path/to/game.zip
--boundary--
